<section class="features">
  <div class="features-inner">
    <div class="section-label">What PolyIC Offers</div>
    <h2>Everything You Need for Polymer Research</h2>
    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🔬</div><h3>PolyCrit Database</h3><p>Searchable records of polymer chromatography conditions, critical ranges, and experimental parameters.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">⚙️</div><h3>Research Tools</h3><p>Interactive calculators and planners to help design and optimize your polymer separation experiments.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">📄</div><h3>Publications</h3><p>Curated literature linked directly to database entries for full traceability from data to source.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🎓</div><h3>Education</h3><p>Video lectures, lab protocols, and reading lists for students and early-career polymer scientists.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

